title: Coming Soon
description:
From Gimlet Media and the creators of HBO's The Jinx, a new podcast exploring the tangled web of crime and corruption in American cities. This season: Providence, Rhode Island. The first episode premieres November 20th. 
Learn more about your ad choices. Visit podcastchoices.com/adchoices
